rs lips, making it impossible to distinguish the movements of them. If a translator is required in some situation, limiting the number of people allowed could deprive a deaf community member of an in-person translator.%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
